// Logout button — the logout sidepanel tab (interface 182), component 6.
// Close any open modal, then request a logout (the engine's process_logouts
// grants it when the player is eligible).
//
// content-old's full handler also blocks logout in a duel / on a gnomeball
// pitch via procs (~in_duel_arena, ~inzone_coord_pair_table) we don't have yet;
// add those guards back when those systems are ported.
[if_button,if_182:com_6]
if_close();
p_logout();
